{"tid":1169581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.9前擱置送中既話 都唔該照樣出嚟","createTime":"2019-05-24T13:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T13:44:55.000Z","uid":216008,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bdc1ce7e51fcf1537b560cda73a0dbfff6ff613","tid":1169581,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"就算6.9之前政府擱置 都請當日企出嚟<br />\n即使外國聯軍出曬聲 都要比國際睇到我地香港係關注呢件事<br />\n而且6.9之前政府擱置 以政府不斷出爾反爾既性格 好大可能只係做比市民睇 過多一排啲團結力散返啲 又隨時用另一個藉口推送中<br />\n中國有一班人想反抗都做唔到<br />\n我地仲有人權自由 就拜託大家唔好眼白白望住我地既香港比人搶走<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"322a3055d2fed25c34de4885589bc26fdc54eb61","tid":1169581,"uid":251086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"彈入 彈出 打我呀笨"},{"pid":"1fe69d4c4998b8e7f2ca62f19665d9eb0cd62dce","tid":1169581,"uid":111692,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31445b8688e541941e10ff40c69c705f9bf0f843","tid":1169581,"uid":180323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe69d4c4998b8e7f2ca62f19665d9eb0cd62dce","tid":1169581,"uid":111692,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"你估到時你會例外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfce8ac1a323b49a62ea6be8cf8ef5eeb35536e0","tid":1169581,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe69d4c4998b8e7f2ca62f19665d9eb0cd62dce","tid":1169581,"uid":111692,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"比人拉有乜問題？你同我一齊比人拉囉 你而家鬧我地廢青即係你鬧緊中國人啦<br />\n條例過左你都唔會好過得去邊架咋五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" c